<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title data-translate="drink-title">Drink & Drive</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="icon.png" type="image/png" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <nav class="nav">
        <div class="nav-container">
          <div class="logo">
            <img src="icon.png" alt="Luxury Transfer logo" class="site-logo" />
            <h2 data-translate="nav-brand">Luxury Transfer</h2>
          </div>
          <ul class="nav-menu">
            <li><a href="index.html" data-translate="nav-home">Начало</a></li>
            <li>
              <a href="index.html#about" data-translate="nav-about">За нас</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="index.html#services" data-translate="nav-services"
                >Услуги</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="index.html#prices" data-translate="nav-prices"
                >Запитване за цена</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="contact.html" data-translate="nav-contact">Контакти</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="drink.html" class="active" data-translate="nav-drink"
                >Drink&Drive</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="language-selector">
              <div class="language-dropdown">
                <button class="language-btn">
                  <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                  <span class="current-lang">BG</span>
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <ul class="language-menu">
                  <li>
                    <a href="#" data-lang="bg" class="active">Български</a>
                  </li>
                  <li><a href="#" data-lang="en">English</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="hamburger">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container" style="padding: 6rem 20px 4rem">
      <section class="drink-hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 data-translate="drink-hero-title">Не карайте пили</h1>
            <p class="lead" data-translate="drink-hero-sub">
              Ако сте пил(а), не рискувайте — обадете ни се и ние ще ви закараме
              безопасно.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <a
                href="tel:+359884497938"
                class="btn btn-primary"
                data-translate="btn-call"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                Обадете се
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-features">
              <div class="feature-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                <span data-translate="drink-feature-1">24/7</span>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                <span data-translate="drink-feature-2"
                  >Професионални шофьори</span
                >
              </div>
              <div class="feature-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <span data-translate="drink-feature-3"
                  >Безопасен транспорт</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="muted-note" data-translate="drink-note">
              Ние сме тук за да ви върнем безопасно у дома.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-content">
          <div class="footer-section">
            <h3>Luxury Transfer</h3>
            <p data-translate="footer-about">
              Вашият надежден партньор за луксозни трансфери от летище София и
              Пловдив.
            </p>
            <div class="social-links">
              <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
              <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
              <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-section">
            <h4 data-translate="footer-contacts">Контакти</h4>
            <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +359 88 4497938</p>
            <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> cotsev0@abv.bg</p>
            <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> София, България</p>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-section">
            <h4 data-translate="footer-services">Услуги</h4>
            <ul>
              <li data-translate="service-sofia-footer">
                Трансфер от летище София
              </li>
              <li data-translate="service-plovdiv-footer">
                Трансфер от летище Пловдив
              </li>
              <li data-translate="service-intercity-footer">
                Междуградски трансфери
              </li>
              <li data-translate="service-international-footer">
                Международни трансфери
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p data-translate="footer-copyright">
            &copy; 2025 Luxury Transfer. Всички права запазени.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
